==Notes==
===Footnotes===
* {{note label|Note1|a|a}} Sources are inconclusive regarding the total amount of Allied shipping sunk. Sources vary between {{GRT|221,981|metric}} and {{GRT|230,781|metric}}.<ref name="Williamson p19"/><ref name="Kurowski p153"/><ref>Alman 1988, p. 281.</ref><ref>Berger 1999, p. 191.</ref> Sometime sources also speak of 17 war-patrols. L<U+00FC>th aborted two patrols on ''U-43'' prematurely after leaving harbour because of oil leakage.<ref>Alman 1988, p. 75,76.</ref>
* {{note label|Note2|b|b}} The German [[Reichsmarine]] was renamed to [[Kriegsmarine]] on 1 June 1935.

